Create project
Install required libraries using CocoaPods. See Podfile.
Create Bridging-Header file and import Objective-C header into Swift code
Add Bridging-Header.h file name to Objective-C Bridging Header section of Build Settings
Configure project on Firebase platform
import JSQMessageViewController and subclass main view controller from it -> input field for message
set up senderId and senderDisplayName in viewDidLoad
override dataSource methods to provide number of messages and info for message

